  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel's restaurant serves a comprehensive buffet continental breakfast each morning with everything from fresh fruit, yogurt, pastries, cereal, selection of cold meats and cheeses, you will also find traditional Italian breakfast cakes. At the far end of the buffet you will find a selection of juices and hot breakfast items including bacon and eggs. </p>
<p>Dinner is made up of four course and there is a choice of options for each. You can also help yourself to the salad buffet available each day but leave rooms for the desert buffet, plenty of sweet treats to choose from. </p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
