  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Breuil is a popular property in <a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a> and brings together guests from all around the world. The hotel team really make the holiday experience special and are always happy to help.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>It's located right by the slopes and a short walk into the centre of town - getting on the mountain couldn't be easier with the Cretaz chairlift in view at the back of the hotel. It links up to the main ski area, giving you easy access to the mountain. The hotel is just steps away from the main streets of Cervinia where you will find everything including bars, restaurant, gift shops and our Inghams ski hire shop. </p>
<h2>Cervinio views</h2>
<p>The rooms are comfortable and some have spectacular views of the Cervinio/Matterhorn. Be sure to take in the views early morning as the sun rises over the mountains and again at night, when the moon lights up one of the most recognisable mountain in all of Europe.</p>
<h2>Facilities</h2>
<p>We love using the spa facilities here after skiing. There's a fitness room, steam room and sauna. Alternatively, head to the spacious bar lounge area serving up a range of Italian drinks including prosecco, Aperol or towards the end of the night, why not try some local grappa.  </p>]]></description>
